Fast-rising Nigerian musician, Joeboy has released a visualiser for his latest single, ‘All For You’ that is off his new extended play (EP), Love and Light. The emPawa singer in this new single delivers a moving ode to love. On this single, he sings about a girl who breaks off with her boyfriend because she is in love with him (Joeboy) and he is all she wants. The singer on the hand feels he is undeserving of her love despite being in love with her as well.  